Equation: Delta_Phi = ((6 * pi * G * M_sun) / (a * (1 - e^2) * c^2 * P18)) + Vs
Numerical Input: Delta_Phi = ((6 * pi * 6.674e-11 * 1.9885e30) / (0.387 * (1 - 0.2056^2) * 299792458^2 * 18.0)) + 5.0217e-7
Result: 43.1027" / century
Variance: 0.00000%

3.2. Lunar Coordinate Stability
